text: Yang In-deok is a South Korean taekwondo practitioner. She won a gold medal in middleweight at the 1991 World Taekwondo Championships in Athens, after defeating Chavela Aaron in the final. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:South Korean female taekwondo practitioners Category:World Taekwondo Championships medalists
